{
  "stem": "4513.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was-- we were there for about a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because what slowed us down was the identification process that the Army was going through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I would say there were several hundred.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what the total count was, but it was several hundred. 'Cause we buried people in mass graves, and we were putting people in in piles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't-- you know, some of these people had numbers on their arm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I assume that's the way they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the numbers only.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know otherwise.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was saying about a month before this happened, we captured about five Germans in a patrol-- what was left of a patrol we had-- in a firefight with--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up just after we crossed the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one-- I-- you know, we searched the prisoners always.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this prisoner had a picture, a picture of a naked woman, nude woman, running across an area with a group of German soldiers standing up laughing as she was running.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a picture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was running toward what I now would identify as a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that was the kind of building that they later talked about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that's my assumption.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have no way of knowing that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Except to know that she was running across this area and somebody took a picture of her with these soldiers looking at her and laughing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I asked them who she was, and they just laughed and said nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I kept the picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I don't know where it is now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought I had it somewhere [INAUDIBLE] locked away in my--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When, you know, the war was almost over, we were headed toward-- we was headed toward the Elbe River.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
